Introduction

BarbieD, formerly known as Kiwi Band and Kiwi Band M, was a female band under Star Road Entertainment. Initially as a band and then as an idol girl group, they debuted under CMG Chorok Stars on December 12, 2014 with the single "Hakunamatata".

On September 7, 2018, they announced that the group would be continuing as a duo after the departure of several members. However, not long after this post, the remaining members Ruby and Saebin left the group, which unofficially confirmed their disbandment.
